author: 95maryo
title: Nice but stiff parking fee
text:
The room was very clean and spacious; located near freeway and restaurants. There was also a refrigerator in the room. Staff was polite and helpful. Hotel is across the street from the bay with a nice walkway along the water.
The only drawback was the $25.00 per day parking fee.
